        "column_zdrTRr": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Scope",
            "description": "<p>Roberto Coin Prestige is a complimentary global protection service created to preserve the beauty and value of your Roberto Coin jewelry over time. Designed to accompany each creation well beyond the moment of purchase, it offers peace of mind against theft, robbery, and irreparable accidental damage. Conceived as a natural extension of the Maison’s commitment to excellence, it ensures that every jewel remains a symbol of lasting elegance.</p>"
          }
        },
        "column_Hfjqcy": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Duration",
            "description": "<p>Valid for two years from the date of purchase, coverage applies under specific conditions to jewelry valued between €1,000 and €100,000 (VAT included). Eligible clients may receive a replacement jewel of equal value through a digital voucher. From December 22, 2025, the service will be available exclusively for selected pieces purchased at Roberto Coin boutiques in Rome and Venice, marking the beginning of a gradual expansion.</p>"
          }
        },
        "column_Vjw864": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Activation",
            "description": "<p>Activation of Roberto Coin Prestige is not automatic; registration on the dedicated digital platform is required at the time of purchase. Once registered, eligible jewelry will appear in the client’s account and be covered according to the applicable terms and conditions. The service is delivered with the technical support of AION, Roberto Coin’s specialized partner, ensuring a secure, seamless, and transparent experience throughout the coverage period.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
