            "title": "Personal Data Processing",
            "text_case": "uppercase",
            "content": "<p>Personal data shall be processed exclusively for purposes related to the management of the Prestige Service, in compliance with the GDPR and applicable data protection laws. The processing shall be carried out by Roberto Coin S.p.A., as Data Controller, and by the technology partner AION Cover S.r.l., as Data Processor. Further details are available in the dedicated Privacy Policy.</p>",
            "show_icon": false,
